    </div>
    
    <div class="thread-card">
        <div class="main-info">
            <div class="profile-pic">
                <img src="/imgs/lego.png" alt="profile picture"/>
            </div>
            <div class="profile-and-post">
                <div class="top-row">
                    <h3>LegoLass</h3>
                    <p>8h</p>
                </div>
                <h5>Inspired by Nature: My LEGO Bonsai</h5>
                <p>I’ve always been inspired by nature, so I decided to build a LEGO bonsai tree this weekend. It’s not an official set, but I used a mix of green pieces and some from the LEGO Flower Bouquet kit. I’d love to see if anyone else has made custom builds inspired by the natural world!</p>
